{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0b0dd9842c","title":"中央关于发表广州军管会和市政府就职布告的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"38e3d6070e","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":15,"articleId":"0b0dd9842c"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji27","name":"毛泽东全集第27卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/27-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji27":{"comments":[{"id":"19c6ee95f8","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"李章达，当时任中央人民政府委员、中国国民党革命委员会中央委员。张村，无党派民主人士。吴奇伟，原国民党政府军将领，1949年5月率部在广东东部、福建西部起义；当时任政协第一届全国委员会委员。"},{"id":"6cfbb0415e","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"叶剑英，当时任中共中央华南分局第一书记。"},{"id":"30b1d79c4d","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"朱光，当时任中共广州市委副书记。"}],"contents":[{"id":"a9b5db5639","type":"title","text":"中央关于发表广州军管会和市政府就职布告的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c"},{"id":"19c6ee95f8","type":"paragraph","text":"华南分局，并告华中局：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c"},{"id":"6cfbb0415e","type":"paragraph","text":"我军即入广州。你们可以奉人民革命军事委员会命令，照前定名单（增加季章达张酿村吴奇伟“三人）立即发表广州军事管制委员会的就职布告，及广州市人民政府（叶剑英为市长，李章达及我方一人为副市长，朱光为秘书长）的就职布告。待中央人民政府委员会开会时再行追认。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c"},{"id":"30b1d79c4d","type":"subtitle","text":"中央西删","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c"}],"page":{"id":"c8cc1a9198","publicationId":"maoquanji27","articleId":"0b0dd9842c","start":418,"end":418}}}},"__N_SSG":true}